<info gid="3068001480" type="Plot Summary">After abandoning their submarine &lt;i&gt;Yamanami&lt;/i&gt; - which collides with a Russian submarine, Captain Shiro Kaieda and his crew are assigned to man a top-secret, U.S./Japanese nuclear vessel codenamed &lt;i&gt;Sea Bat&lt;/i&gt;. However, during the &lt;i&gt;Sea Bat&lt;/i&gt;'s maiden voyage, Kaieda sends the submarine off its plotted course, causing a diplomatic rift between the U.S. and Japanese governments - who fight over possession of the vessel. The situation is further complicated when Kaieda renames the submarine &lt;i&gt;Yamato&lt;/i&gt; and declares it an independent nation.</info>
